UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS HB 1/VO
1 (2) The Secretary of State shall publish the associated administrative regulations and
2 other applicable guidance issued by the United States Secretary of the Treasury
3 or the Internal Revenue Service on the Secretary of State's website.
4 (3) The Secretary of State may promulgate administrative regulations in accordance
5 with KRS Chapter 13A necessary to carry out this section.
6 (4) The Secretary of State shall collect a fee from scholarship granting organizations
7 or accept private contributions to pay the necessary costs of administration of this
8 section. All amounts received under this subsection shall be deposited in a
9 restricted fund account, not commingled, and shall be used solely to administer
10 this section.
11 (5) Any immunity under the Eleventh Amendment to the Constitution of the United
12 States is waived under this section.
